      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/618074396_17949946380071437_1930967160697104237_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;ig_cache_key=MzE5MjE4NTc3ODEzMjk2Mjg0OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=iTzzSbEo_RgQ7kNvwFHDYvf&amp;_nc_oc=Adq0XwM0oc8jkWOJG5quR50o86oxY9ue4HKIa_TDpKetbiYO1GlcnCHbSEDrlMmwhDs&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=uVsAmbxJJL4ZgPdsIdhAkA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwEOimW7_llhpADG872FnekWDqqksNG_hyHOqHcGJEjow&amp;oe=69CA1CC2" alt="Instagram billede fra @cocoowino" /></p><p><strong>@cocoowino</strong></p><p>‘SHARING IS CARING’ is out and available on all platforms. I am way too emotional today, to get into what this project means to me. What matters now, is what it’s going to mean to you. I sincerely hope it will resonate and give comfort and joy.<br/>
